 About Saxe Mortgage
Company
Saxe Mortgage Company was first
founded in 1938 with humble beginnings and has over the years grown
into the leading private money mortgage lender in the San Francisco
Bay Area. We offer a host of different services to help
individuals, brokers, and more in our community.
Do you need a loan but you
don’t necessarily want to go through a big bank? Come to Saxe
Mortgage Company instead! We specialize in short-term real estate
financing for residential, commercial, multi-family, mixed-use, and
construction loans. This way you can get the loan that you need and
purchase the property that you want in little to no time. We have
recently funded many properties throughout our community, and you
can be next!
