Money
Commercial Hard
Money 




Commercial
Lending 
Hard Money
Hard Money Bridge
Hard Money 2nds
Private Money 2nds





Contact
Us Today!
We pride ourselves on our fast
closings, our integrity, and how we are broker-friendly. How do we
do it? We finance your real estate transactions through private
investor capital. Private money lending has increased exponentially
over the past years, which allows us to provide loans to our
clients.
Through our loan application
process, we will help you decide which type of loan is best for
your needs. Our experienced and professional team is here to help
you every step of the way.
 

Here at Saxe Mortgage Company,
we pay our investors 9+% secured by the best equity-rich real
estate in the most stable market, the San Francisco Bay Area. If
you are interested in learning more about our investment
opportunities or you’re interested in learning more about our
available loans, please give us a call. We look forward to talking
with you in the near future.



